AE silence-Sound of Silence (as per silence) to all enemies within 100'.<br>
<br>
Deftdance-Denon's Dance; Deftdance, as per the disc.<br>
<br>
AE stun-Chord of Chaos; all mobs stunned for 1 second, no save, no damage done to target, unresistable.  (can't break mezz)<br>
<br>
Mana-Manaburst; 200 (or more) mana to all group members (AE version?) Can be doubled as per a critical hit.<br>
<br>
Pet proc-Dirge of Duplicity; each proc produces a pet that looks like the Bard. Each lasts 10 seconds- dps could be the same as the Bard wielding the weapon.<br>
<br>
Focus enhancer-adds 10% to all focus effects, including instrument mods for Bards; stacks with everything. Overfocus essentially.<br>
<br>
Spell reflection-Melanie's Mirror, 100% spell reflect. Lasts 15 seconds. AE?<br>
<br>
Right-click effects:<br>
Ward-Melody of Mercy; when cast creates a ward that regens everyone's mana and hitpoints at twice the rate of any Bard songs (AE or group) that are playing within range. Stacks with all other wards/regen.<br>
<br>
Taunt-Whisp of Whimsy; summons a ball of energy that instantly aggros anything within range and leads it away for a short (30 seconds?) duration.<br>
<br>
Group double attack-Agilmente's Aria of Attack; all group members (including the Bard) receive double attack as per the ability.<br>
<br>
Focus effects:<br>
Mana preservation-Melanie's Melody of Mana; Fading Memories, charm songs, DDD use less mana. Could also allow the Bard wielding it to receive the benefits of all mana regen spells and songs.<br>
<br>
Instrument focus-Rizlona's Remarkable Riff; If the weapon is wielded with an instrument, the equipped instrument's mod is increased by 50% (or more).<br>
<br>
Missed notes-Denon's Dilligence; the wielder will not miss notes. Period.<br>
<br>
<br>
