<br>
I think the real problem isn't that our old epic was used so long, but that it was used so long while also denying us use of better weapons.  If the old epic was in any other slot, we'd simply be used to it.  Its really easy to leave old gear in an armor slot because we have so many, and they are passive in nature.  You only have 2 weapon slots, and you notice their activity with all the red spam.  after 5 expansions not being able to increase your red spam with everybody else is draining on the morale.<br>
