<br>
Why not have the epic rewards be augs? <br>
<br>
With the upcoming patch allowing augments to be removable (without being destroyed), this would extend the viability of the reward for a long time.<br>
<br>
Extending this idea:<br>
<br>
Maybe give us a base item (charm/range would be perfect imo) with decent stats, and X aug slots. The end reward gives us &gt;X augs, where we can customize the base item how we want. Maybe it has 3 slots, where we can put a single instrument type mod, a voice mod, a choice of clickies, etc. I am not sugesting giving us all possible options, but it would allow for customizing without creating tons of variations of said rewards.<br>
